Actress, Regina Daniels, has expressed her excitement at the gift of $100,000 that she got from her husband, Ned Nwoko. In a post on her Instagram Stories on Thursday, the actress said she had no idea her account had been credited since Wednesday. ALSO READ: Lady arrested for stealing N200k from a store She shared a screenshot of the credit alert and said, “Okay! Can’t believe an alert of 100,000 usd was sitting pretty in my account since yesterday afternoon and I’m just discovering this my husband has lots of mind blowing doings up his sleeve mehnnnnn thank you baby.”  